c: 9
v: 28
t: "Hini na nina bakholwayo! Inene abakhonzi bezithixo bakukungcola. Ke ngoko musani ukubavumela basondele eMasjid eNgcwele (eMakkah) emva kwalo unyaka, kananjalo ukuba noyika ukuhlwempuzeka, uAllâh Uya kuninika indyebo ukuba Uthandile, evela kubuBele baKhe. Inene uAllâh nguSolwazi, uSobulumko"